data.description: One level living with Lake Access! 3 bed, 2bath, Open Concept home with lovely Cathedral ceilings. Outside you will find a private back porch to enjoy those nice Spring days approaching, plenty of storage with a detached garage, as well as a large shed. A large flat lot that would be great for children or pets to play. A great property, at an affordable price! Property is sold as-is, where is. Get in to see it today!
